  "title": "Account Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Daily update on all payment received and matching with invoices in accounting system</li>\n  <li>Daily merchants settlement including Nets and Credit Cards</li>\n  <li>Assist relationship manager on customer payment via credicard for pre-payment transactions</li>\n  <li>Recording for daily cash &amp; cheque received. Cheque scanning into company shared drive &amp; dropping cheques</li>\n  <li>COD / Trade account creation</li>\n  <li>Reminding of customers/relationship manager for overdue invoices</li>\n  <li>Preparation of CTC invoices and account related matters to customer whenever customer/Relationship Manager are requesting</li>\n  <li>Monthly reconciliation of Redmart, Zalora, Amazon and NTUC matching</li>\n</ul>",
